3.10	Paul_W_S_Anderson	Paul W. S. Anderson	Paul William Scott Anderson (born 4 March 1965), also known as Paul W. S. Anderson or Paul Anderson, is an English film director who regularly works in science fiction movies and video game adaptations.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Paul_W._S._Anderson_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg/220px-Paul_W._S._Anderson_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg
